"title": "5030: knowledge, of Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5030: knowledge, of jesus christ",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The believer's understanding and experience of Jesus Christ, which arises from a personal relationship established through faith.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the supreme revelation of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6-John14:10\">JHN 14:6–14:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:27\">MAT 11:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">JHN 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:19\">JHN 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:26\">JHN 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:20\">COL 1:15–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of Jesus Christ acquired through a personal relationship with him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:42\">JHN 4:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:4-Matt9:8\">MAT 9:4–9:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:8-Mark2:12\">MRK 2:8–2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:22-Luke5:26\">LUK 5:22–5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:38\">JHN 10:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:11\">JHN 14:11</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of Jesus Christ acquired through the work of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1CO 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:6-1John5:9\">1JN 5:6–5:9</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of Jesus Christ is associated with knowing God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:26\">JHN 17:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:19\">JHN 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14-John10:15\">JHN 10:14–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27-John10:30\">JHN 10:27–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6-John14:11\">JHN 14:6–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:15\">JHN 15:15</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of Jesus Christ should increase consistently</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:8\">2PE 1:5–1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Consequences of knowing Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Reconciliation with God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:19-2Cor5:20\">2CO 5:19–5:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:16\">EPH 2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Access to God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">ROM 5:1–5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:18\">EPH 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Becoming like Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Peace</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">ROM 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:14-Eph2:18\">EPH 2:14–2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Hope</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17-Eph1:18\">EPH 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27-John10:28\">JHN 10:27–10:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:13\">1JN 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Renewal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:19-Eph4:22\">EPH 4:19–4:22</a></p>\n<h3>Unity among believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:21\">JHN 17:21</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection by the world</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:18-John15:21\">JHN 15:18–15:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:2-John16:3\">JHN 16:2–16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of Jesus Christ is to manifest itself in obedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:3-1John2:6\">1JN 2:3–2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:21–7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:31–25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4-John15:5\">JHN 15:4–15:5</a></p>",
